# Textbook source assets — large binaries (videos, PPTX, audio) that
# exceed GitHub's 100 MB push limit. The design-image PNGs derived
# from these (under each lesson's `design/` subfolder) are committed
# so the LKP URLs resolve in the backend's static mount; the raw
# sources stay on the researcher's machine.
frontend/src/assets/textbook-assets/**/*.mp4
frontend/src/assets/textbook-assets/**/*.pptx
frontend/src/assets/textbook-assets/**/*.mp3

